{
  "type": "doc",
  "content": [
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
        "level": 1,
        "uid": "UidgrRPV001"
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Introduction"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "attrs": {
        "uid": "UidgrRPV002"
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "This document outlines the design and implementation of a "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "bold"
            }
          ],
          "text": "new REST API"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": ". The purpose of this API is to provide a standardized interface for accessing and manipulating data related to a specific domain. The API will conform to the principles of Representational State Transfer (REST) architecture style."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
        "level": 1,
        "uid": "UidgrRPV003"
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Design"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
        "level": 2,
        "uid": "UidgrRPV004"
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Resource Design"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "attrs": {
        "uid": "UidgrRPV005"
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The API will be designed around resources, each of which represents a domain entity. Resources will be identified using URIs (Uniform Resource Identifiers). The following URIs will be used for the API:"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "bulletList",
      "attrs": {
        "uid": "UidgrRPV006"
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "attrs": {
            "uid": "UidgrRPV007"
          },
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "attrs": {
                "uid": "UidgrRPV008"
              },
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "code"
                    }
                  ],
                  "text": "/api/{version}/{resource}/{id}"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " – to retrieve, update, or delete a specific entity."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "attrs": {
            "uid": "UidgrRPV009"
          },
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "attrs": {
                "uid": "UidgrRPV010"
              },
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "code"
                    }
                  ],
                  "text": "/api/{version}/{resource}"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " – to retrieve a list of entities or create a new entity."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
        "level": 2,
        "uid": "UidgrRPV011"
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Response Formats"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "attrs": {
        "uid": "UidgrRPV012"
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The API will support both JSON and XML data formats for responses. The response format can be specified in the request headers."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "codeBlock",
      "attrs": {
        "language": "json",
        "uid": "UidgrRPV013"
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "{\n  \"data\": {\n    \"id\": 1234,\n    \"name\": \"Specfy\",\n    \"yc\": true,\n    \"tags\": [\"documentation\", \"developers\"]\n  }\n}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
        "level": 1,
        "uid": "UidgrRPV014"
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Conclusion"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
