            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Ut semper eros ipsum, eget rutrum nisi consequat vitae.",
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "attrs": {
        "uid": "UidgrRPV015"
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "This document outlines the design and implementation of a new REST API. The API is designed to provide a standardized interface for accessing and manipulating data related to a specific domain. The API conforms to REST architecture style and supports secure access through an authentication and authorization mechanism."
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
